{"tid":1376840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗鐵回應左721 車長們幾時出聲明回應罷工??","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:51.000Z","uid":55105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbba92ccbcc1ce57ce6e9fcbaabae37a41f1bd85","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>狗鐵回應:</strong><br />\n［突發］港鐵出左內部文件回應車長罷工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373335</a><br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n狗鐵對721嘅回應我相信冇人會收貨<br />\n有冇人識朋友做車長? 係咪係時候向全港市民公佈罷工安排???<br />\n利申: 強烈<span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>地鐵帶頭罷工癱瘓全港<br />\n<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<strong>車長們較早前嘅聯署:</strong><br />\n[MTR 遍地開花] 東鐵綫車長的心聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362704</a><br />\n[MTR遍地開花] 將軍澳綫車長心聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360733</a><br />\n［遍地開花］港島綫車長致港鐵管理層的公開信<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365151</a><br />\n［MTR遍地開花］西鐵馬鐵線車長心聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361051</a><br />\n［MTR遍地開花］一眾東鐵綫列車車長實名聯署聲明<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370545</a><br />\n（MTR遍地開花）港島綫列車車長就7月21日於元朗站發生恐襲事件之聲明<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370186</a><br />\n［遍地開花］100名機場快綫及東涌綫車長發表開名聯署，佔全綫77.5%<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370979</a>"},{"pid":"9a12994d68d1d1b21db5235f320cbe6761975648","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dfc591078293558c1360dea02d22b242124fc5f","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f7b84f94d9a00b4e527723850cf3c5c99f9841e","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1212a1dbac21b5769de9fe22bad2d2f794b19894","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24b450afa5131d438b02bc53a9c21511f4ed14eb","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3bcda71cf3268350edb4411996d61eca29c92d4","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba3043796c0a95e79d6f0a6a897dd73b5584a9fc","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c7f0b3ad3b37bc4fbb193e982fe51a7895a94c0","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3ce6ab064c78232a8d86f06ee30eec237070dd","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b6f254e49931807e994c1ae53368a2391948f05","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7b7031df413fb00972eb9e57816a411dee8a294","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d2b23b88ba71f883c5afddaf30a041130f967c7","tid":1376840,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"推"